01:34:13.743 --> 01:34:16.209
for Michael's life, but really,

01:34:16.210 --> 01:34:18.311
I'd been holding out for healing

01:34:18.312 --> 01:34:21.910
and when it didn't come, I was lost,

01:34:21.911 --> 01:34:24.345
but in my sorrow, I missed
the truly powerful thing

01:34:24.346 --> 01:34:27.012
that had happened right
in front of my eyes.

01:34:29.813 --> 01:34:32.212
In life, Michael was a teacher.

01:34:32.213 --> 01:34:34.080
He taught people how to protect themselves

01:34:34.113 --> 01:34:36.646
and respect others.

01:34:36.647 --> 01:34:37.947
He showed them what it meant to be

01:34:37.948 --> 01:34:41.148
a true and giving friend,
and even where you could get

01:34:41.149 --> 01:34:44.081
the best barbecue ribs.

01:34:44.082 --> 01:34:47.582
He helped a brother see the
light through the darkness.

01:34:50.317 --> 01:34:52.449
But the most important lesson was the one

01:34:52.450 --> 01:34:56.582
he made so clear to us in
his life and death trial,

01:34:56.583 --> 01:34:59.284
the power of real faith.

01:35:13.653 --> 01:35:16.453
- Mr. Fenton, you
were wrong when you said

01:35:16.454 --> 01:35:18.586
God wouldn't answer me that night.

01:35:18.587 --> 01:35:21.087
He did, He sent you.

01:35:21.088 --> 01:35:22.922
Thank you for being a true friend.

01:35:22.956 --> 01:35:24.988
Michael.

